# MathScript Spring Boot Migration Rules

## Target Stack
Spring Boot 3.3, Java 21 (LTS), Maven, Spring Data JPA, PostgreSQL (HikariCP), Spring Security

## Directory Structure
```
spring-backend/
  pom.xml
  src/main/java/com/mathscript/
    MathscriptApplication.java        # @SpringBootApplication entry point
    config/
      CorsConfig.java                 # CORS configuration (replaces FastAPI CORSMiddleware)
      SecurityConfig.java             # Spring Security config
    controller/
      SessionController.java          # GET/POST /api/session/*
      StoryController.java            # POST /api/story (AI generation)
      ShopController.java             # POST /api/shop/*
      StripeController.java           # POST /api/stripe/* (webhook)
      HealthController.java           # GET /health
    service/
      GeminiService.java              # Google Gemini HTTP client
      OpenAiService.java              # OpenAI HTTP client
      ElevenLabsService.java          # ElevenLabs TTS HTTP client
      StripeService.java              # Stripe operations
      SessionService.java             # Session CRUD + HMAC signing
      DatabaseService.java            # User + usage DB operations
    model/
      entity/UserSession.java         # JPA entity (maps to users table)
      dto/StoryRequest.java           # Request DTOs (replaces pydantic models)
      dto/StoryResponse.java          # Response DTOs
      dto/SessionDto.java
    repository/
      UserSessionRepository.java      # Spring Data JPA repository
    util/
      HmacUtil.java                   # HMAC session signing (replaces Python sign_session_id)
  src/main/resources/
    application.yml                   # Config (reads env vars)
  src/test/java/com/mathscript/
    controller/SessionControllerTest.java
```

## application.yml Pattern
```yaml
server:
  port: 8080

spring:
  datasource:
    url: ${DATABASE_URL}
    driver-class-name: org.postgresql.Driver
  jpa:
    hibernate:
      ddl-auto: update
    database-platform: org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQLDialect

app:
  gemini-api-key: ${GEMINI_API_KEY}
  openai-api-key: ${OPENAI_API_KEY}
  elevenlabs-api-key: ${ELEVENLABS_API_KEY}
  session-secret: ${SESSION_SECRET}
  stripe-secret-key: ${STRIPE_SECRET_KEY}
  stripe-webhook-secret: ${STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET}
```

## Endpoint Mapping (Python → Java)
| Python FastAPI                     | Spring Controller Method             |
|------------------------------------|--------------------------------------|
| GET /api/session/{id}              | @GetMapping("/api/session/{id}")     |
| POST /api/story                    | @PostMapping("/api/story")           |
| POST /api/shop/buy                 | @PostMapping("/api/shop/buy")        |
| POST /api/stripe/webhook           | @PostMapping("/api/stripe/webhook")  |
| GET /api/pdf/{id}                  | @GetMapping("/api/pdf/{id}")         |
| GET /health                        | @GetMapping("/health")               |

