        // Return rawId + "." + hex12chars
    }
    public static String verify(String signedId, String secret) {
        // Split on last ".", recompute, compare with MessageDigest.isEqual()
        // Return rawId or throw UnauthorizedException
    }
}
```

## AI API Calls in Java
Use Spring WebClient (reactive) or OkHttp3 for external AI API calls:
```java
@Service
public class GeminiService {
    // POST to https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/...
    // Use WebClient with timeout and retry
    // Return Mono<StoryResponse> or block() for simplicity
}
```

## Stripe Webhook Security
```java
// MUST verify signature — equivalent to Python stripe.Webhook.construct_event()
String sigHeader = request.getHeader("Stripe-Signature");
Event event = Webhook.constructEvent(payload, sigHeader, webhookSecret);
```

## Migration Order
1. [ ] Phase 1: Health + Characters endpoints (no DB, no AI)
2. [ ] Phase 2: Session GET/POST + DB schema (JPA entities + migration)
3. [ ] Phase 3: Shop endpoints
4. [ ] Phase 4: Stripe endpoints (most security-critical)
5. [ ] Phase 5: AI story + image generation (largest, most complex)
6. [ ] Phase 6: PDF generation + ElevenLabs TTS
7. [ ] Phase 7: Switch nginx upstream from :5000 → :8080
8. [ ] Phase 8: Remove Python backend

