## DO NOT
- Do not rewrite Python backend until Phase 1-4 are tested and working
- Do not use Spring MVC Thymeleaf templates — frontend is React (SPA)
- Do not store API keys in application.yml directly — always use ${ENV_VAR}
- Do not use `ddl-auto: create-drop` in production — use `update` or Flyway migrations
